Summary

The project is a Maven archetype for basic Servlet 3.0 based Java web application. None dependencies to any web framework - just plain Java Servlet
no XML. Jetty plugin included - gets your application running in seconds.

Default idea is taken from: https://github.com/maciejwalkowiak/servlet3-maven-archetype.git

Installation:
1. Clone this repository 

$ git clone https://github.com/tomascejka/arch-mvn_servlet3-webapp-jetty.git

2. Install it to local Maven repository

$ cd servlet3.0-maven-archetype
$ mvn install

3. Create project based on this archetype:

$ mvn archetype:generate \
    -DarchetypeGroupId=cz.tomascejka.archetypes \
    -DarchetypeArtifactId=servlet3-webapp-jetty-archetype \
    -DarchetypeVersion=1.0

Run project:

$ mvn jetty:run